    <description>Flow calculates the end month of the curriculum by adding the term length, in months, to the curriculum&apos;s start date. The calculation accounts for varying lengths of months and leap years to accurately determine the end date. (Sprint 10)
06/27/25 - PE - Added logic to stamp current date to Delayed Start Timestamp when stage is moved to Delayed Start</description>
    <environments>Default</environments>
    <formulas>
        <description>This formula calculates the end month of the curriculum by adding the term length, in months, to the curriculum&apos;s start date. The calculation accounts for varying lengths of months and leap years to accurately determine the end date.</description>
        <name>FormulaEndMonth</name>
        <dataType>Date</dataType>
        <expression>ADDMONTHS({!$Record.Curriculum_Start_Month__c},{!$Record.Term_Length_Months__c})</expression>
    </formulas>
